Apple has released iOS 11.4 for compatible devices. The new version of iOS includes AirPlay 2 multi-room audio, support for HomePod stereo pairs, and Messages in iCloud. “This update also includes bug fixes and improvements,” said Apple. When accessed by MyBroadband, the update was 306.5MB in size for the iPhone X. Details of the latest features in iOS 11.4 are listed below. For information on the security content of Apple software updates, user can visit the Apple support page.